                  greater spatial detail than previously available, is
                  used to train a land cover classification data set
                  obtained by merging two different satellite-derived
                  products (Boston University’s MODIS-derived land
                  cover product and the GLC2000 data set). Our data
                  are presented at 5 min ($\sim$10 km) spatial resolution
