                  (90\% confidence range of 12.2–17.1) million km2 of
                  cropland (12\% of the Earth’s ice-free land surface)
                  and 28.0 (90\% confidence range of 23.6–30.0)
                  million km2 of pasture (22\%) in the year 2000.},
